BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Stop The Data Center Coming To Martindale Brightwood
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260315T190000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260315T210000Z
UID:bada8a0d5596c7038b03843af3300bff@mobilize.us
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mobilize-uploads-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/u
 ploads/event/Data%20Center%203_20260222170408057178.jpg
DESCRIPTION:We need you to help pressure your city-county councilor to hel
 p stop the Data Center coming to Martindale Brightwood. Our partners have 
 spoken with hundreds of residents and mobilized with community partners to
  oppose this project. There is no support for it\, but Councilor Ron Gibso
 n is committed to delivering on behalf of the developer. Join us - and Mat
 t Davis of LiveFree Indiana - in contacting Martindale Brightwood resident
 s to: 1) Alert them to the possible construction of the data center\, 
LOCATION:Brightwood Community Center\, 4062 E 34th St\, Indianapolis\, IN\
 , 46218
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/indivisiblecentralindiana/event/909383/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Central Indiana (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
