BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:ACLU-IN Volunteer Social
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260507T213000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260507T233000Z
UID:5acfbe37410bdb638ed2940ee558718a@mobilize.us
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mobilize-uploads-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/u
 ploads/event/LO%20Training%20Header%20%282%29_20260203214202889969.png
DESCRIPTION:Join us in Indianapolis for a special ACLU of Indiana Voluntee
 r Social! Whether you're fired up about protecting civil liberties\, ready
  to stand up for LGBTQ+ rights\, or just curious about how to get involved
  — we want to meet you. Learn how you can get involved and stay engaged.
  Dinner and N/A drinks provided! Please register to see the event details.
LOCATION:Indianapolis\, IN
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/acluin/event/896878/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Central Indiana (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Indivisible Northeast Indiana No Kings Volunteer Training
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260321T170000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260321T190000Z
UID:a098a5a6657b3c5316a756fffa0f9375@mobilize.us
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mobilize-uploads-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/u
 ploads/event/WE%20HAVE%20FRIENDS%20EVERYWHERE_20260305193518417398.png
DESCRIPTION:## Let's get ready for No Kings 3! Saturday March 21 will be t
 raining day for our volunteer team in preparation for the No Kings rally t
 he following weekend. The first shift\, from 1pm-3pm\, is for our crew\, p
 hotographers\, table monitors\, data collectors\, information handout pers
 onnel and anyone who isn't a safety marshal. The second shift\, from 3pm-5
 :30pm is specifically for those wanting to be safety marshals. Feel free t
 o sign up for both trainings if you desire to do more with Indivisible Nor
 t
LOCATION:Allen County Public Library - Main\, 900 Library Plz\, Rooms A-B\
 , Fort Wayne\, IN\, 46802
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/indivisiblenortheastindiana/event/915472/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Central Indiana (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
