BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:New Volunteer Orientation
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260324T160000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260324T163000Z
UID:39e6a7299a14096be31d60ced3168033@mobilize.us
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mobilize-uploads-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/u
 ploads/event/Statehouse%20Rally%20121_20251209201613606685.png
DESCRIPTION:This is the next step to getting plugged into ACLU of Indiana 
 Volunteer opportunities. Register for this webinar to get trained on what 
 it means to be a volunteer with the ACLU of Indiana. Sign up for a time th
 at works for you! Once you have attended one New Volunteer Orientation you
  do not need to sign up again. These happen on a quarterly basis to get pe
 ople trained and signed up!
LOCATION:Virtual event
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/acluin/event/876028/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Central Indiana (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
